Parker & Quinn is the signature restaurant of the
Refinery Hotel. New York’s energy and authenticity are
palpable at this modern American bistro that channels
Gotham’s grit and glamour. Just like New York City,
Parker & Quinn is inherently American with a global
appeal, meant to transcend decades with design
touches spanning 1920’s New York through present day.
Parker & Quinn is a gathering place for all, where solo
travelers and large groups are equally welcome.
